{"tid":1217113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】仇思達支持周日遊行！","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:32:34.000Z","uid":142242,"like":20,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de23cb90ce0b40a5a9268c265d5beca53281751d","tid":1217113,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"仇思達facebook：<br />\n<br />\n民陣發起周日再次遊行，我是支持的，適合一家大細、扶老攜幼參與──只要「泛民」停止籌款，以及孔令瑜、費高陳等不再以大台姿態做「架兩」。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼心態上會調整呢？一、遊行的成本極低，就算白行一趟，也只是損失了一個休息日（假如有效就更加好啦）；二、即使特府當晚又發聲明，表明將會恢復二讀，遊行亦可以證明遊行是無效的。這是非常重要的，將會使更多的市民同情行動派，加強了「和理非」和激進兩條路線的互諒與包容。6&middot;12的槍聲已經驚醒和震憾了「和理非」，香港人爭氣！<br />\n<br />\n#首次認同遊行"},{"pid":"64d295226ff7c29f7c248690f88eabf1dac4c31a","tid":1217113,"uid":12510,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:02:54.000Z","msg":"支持佢呢個post, 但佢個人就食屎喇"},{"pid":"485e389ae04ec18f5767475ca34845c7f3956fe3","tid":1217113,"uid":4783,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"64d295226ff7c29f7c248690f88eabf1dac4c31a","tid":1217113,"uid":12510,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:02:54.000Z","msg":"支持佢呢個post, 但佢個人就食屎喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n支持大家出去遊行<br />\n但大灣駒就算撚數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ac8759bedc33b914c7bf927fc3593b7283509c","tid":1217113,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"唔捐錢邊有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83da33c6621eb2b4ac0edfb07ca2061564643dec","tid":1217113,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"條友搞咩又正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1279b2eabb08b2a1b70f75355bb35e38e82b9b1","tid":1217113,"uid":91721,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"83da33c6621eb